race.comment: GO GETTEM CROKER (2) recorded a 4 length win (16.86) in a Grade 4/5 last time at this track. Looks the one to beat with even luck. BLACKPOOL RANGER (3) lines up chasing another win after scoring over 300m at this track in 16.95, set up by a brilliant early sectional. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Can make it two on the bounce. PRINCESS MILA (1) has missed the frame at her last couple but wasn't beaten far three back when third (17.16) at this track in a Free For All. Has the ability and expected to do much better. ELITE GENERAL (8) will be hard to beat with a drop in distance.
